<verse number="22" style="v" />I will declare your name to my brothers;</para>

<para style="q1">in the midst of the assembly I will praise you.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="23" style="v" />You who fear Yahweh, praise him!</para>

<para style="q1">All you descendants of Jacob, honor him!</para>

<para style="q1">Stand in awe of him, all you descendants of Israel!</para>
